snippet.title: The Walking Dead: Our World Coming July 12 to iOS and Android
snippet.description:
The Walking Dead: Our World, first-of-a-kind location based augmented reality mobile game will hit Apple App Store and Google Play on July 12! 

Fight walkers on the streets, in the park, on your sofa, wherever and whenever you feel like it. You don’t need to face the apocalypse alone; Rick, Daryl, Michonne and all your favorite characters from AMC’s The Walking Dead will fight by your side.

Pre-register at The Walking Dead: Our World at GETOURWORLD.COM
